    <li><strong>Legacy Projects:</strong> Many wealthy individuals engage in philanthropic efforts to give back to society. This could mean starting a foundation or actively supporting local charities and initiatives.</li>
    <li><strong>Cultural Engagement:</strong> Wealth can also lead to a deeper appreciation for the arts and culture. Attending operas, gallery openings, or charity galas becomes a frequent occurrence, enhancing their social circles.</li>
</ul>
